OL,3,COfficer won't face charges following
OL,4,Cteenagers' deaths which sparked riots
OL,6,FA South Wales Police officer who was
OL,7,Fdriving a van following two teenage
OL,8,Fboys who subsequently died in an e-
OL,9,Fbike crash will not face criminal
OL,10,Fcharges, the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,11,Fhas said.
OL,13,FKyrees Sullivan, 16, and Harvey Evans,
OL,14,F15, died in May 2023, minutes after
OL,15,FCCTV captured them being followed by
OL,16,Fthe police van.
