OL,6,FAnother officer, a passenger in the
OL,7,Fpolice van, was also previously served
OL,8,Fwith a gross misconduct notice.
OL,10,FMalcolm McHaffie, Head of the Crown
OL,11,FProsecution Service Special Crime
OL,12,FDivision, said: "Our thoughts remain
OL,13,Fwith the families and friends of the
OL,14,Ftwo teenagers following their tragic
OL,15,Fdeaths in May 2023.
